ty|Democratic and Social Centre \u2013 People's Party]]<br>{{lang|pt|Centro Democr\u00e1tico e Social \u2013 Partido Popular}}\n|CDS-PP\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{Composition bar|5|230|#0093DD}}\n|{{no|Opposition}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |{{ROM}}\n|[[National Liberal Party (Romania)|National Liberal Party]]<br>{{lang|ro|Partidul Na\u021bional Liberal}}\n|PNL\n|{{Composition bar|78|329|#FFDD00}}\n|{{Composition bar|27|136|#FFDD00}}\n|{{yes|Government}}\n|-\n|[[Democratic Alliance of Hungarians in Romania]]<br>{{lang|hu|Rom\u00e1niai Magyar Demokrata Sz\u00f6vets\u00e9g}}<br>{{lang|ro|Uniunea Democrat\u0103 Maghiar\u0103 din Rom\u00e2nia}}\n|UDMR\n|{{Composition bar|21|329|#296633}}\n|{{Composition bar|9|136|#296633}}\n|{{Yes-No|Confidence and Supply}}\n|-\n|[[People's Movement Party]]<br>{{lang|ro|Partidul Mi\u0219carea Popular\u0103}}\n|PMP\n|{{Composition bar|13|329|#90ee90}}\n|{{Composition bar|5|136|#90ee90}}\n|{{Yes-No|Confidence and Supply}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |{{SVK}}\n|[[Christian Democratic Movement]]<br>{{lang|sk|Kres\u0165anskodemokratick\u00e9 hnutie}}\n|KDH\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{Composition bar|0|150|{{European People's Party/meta/color}}}}\n|{{maybe|No Status}}\n|-\n|[[Most\u2013H\u00edd]]\n|\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{Composition bar|0|150|#F58120}}\n|{{no|Extra parliamentary}}\n|-\n|[[Ordinary People (Slovakia)|Ordinary People and Independent personalities]]<br>{{lang|sk|Oby\u010dajn\u00ed \u013dudia a Nez\u00e1visl\u00e9 Osobnosti}}\n|O\u013daNO\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{Composition bar|53|150|#1BB100}}\n|{{yes|Government}}\n|-\n|[[Party of the Hungarian Community]]<br>{{lang|hu|Magyar K\u00f6z\u00f6ss\u00e9g P\u00e1rtja}}<br>{{lang|sk|Strana ma\u010farskej komunity}}\n|SMK/MKP\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{Composition bar|0|150|{{European People's Party/meta/color}}}}\n|{{maybe|No Status}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |{{SVN}}\n|[[Slovenian Democratic Party]]<br>{{lang|sl|Slovenska demokratska stranka}}\n|SDS\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{Composition bar|26|90|#fcda00}}\n|{{yes|Government}}\n|-\n|[[Slovenian People's Party]]<br>{{lang|sl|Slovenska ljudska stranka}}\n|SLS\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{Composition bar|0|90|{{European People's Party/meta/color}}}}\n|{{maybe|non-parliamentary, but Government}}\n|-\n|[[New Slovenia|New Slovenia\u2013Christian Democrats]]<br>{{lang|sl|Nova Slovenija \u2013 Kr\u0161\u010danski demokrati}}\n|NSi\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{Composition bar|7|90|#009ac9}}\n|{{yes|Government}}\n|-\n|{{ESP}}\n|[[People's Party (Spain)|People's Party]]<br>{{lang|es|Partido Popular}}\n|PP\n|{{Composition bar|89|350|#1D84CE}}\n|{{Composition bar|97|265|#1D84CE}}\n|{{no|Opposition}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{SWE}}\n|[[Moderate Party]]<br>{{lang|sv|Moderata samlingspartiet}}\n| {{Moderate Party/meta/abbr}}\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{Composition bar|70|349|#019CDB}}\n|{{no|Opposition}}\n|-\n|[[Christian Democrats (Sweden)|Christian Democrats]]<br>{{lang|sv|Kristdemokraterna}}\n| {{Christian Democrats (Sweden)/meta/abbr}}\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{Composition bar|22|349|#2D338E}}\n|{{no|Opposition}}\n|}\n\n=== Suspended members ===\n{{HUN}}\n* [[Fidesz]] (as of 20 March 2019)<ref name=\"Fid-EPP\">{{cite web|title=European center right suspends Hungarian PM Orb\u00e1n|url=https://www.politico.eu/article/orbans-party-suspended-from-european-peoples-party/|accessdate=20 March 2019}}</ref>\n\n=== Associate members ===\n{{ALB}}\n* [[Democratic Party of Albania]] (PDSh)\n\n{{NMK}}\n* [[Internal Macedonian Revolutionary Organization \u2013 Democratic Party for Macedonian National Unity]] (VMRO\u2013DPMNE)\n\n{{NOR}}\n* [[Conservative Party (Norway)|Conservative Party]] (H)\n\n{{SRB}}\n* [[Serbian Progressive Party]] (SNS)\n* [[Alliance of Vojvodina Hungarians]] (VMSZ/SVM)\n\n{{CHE}}\n* [[Christian Democratic People's Party of Switzerland|Christian Democratic People's Party]] (CVP)\n\n=== Observer members ===\n{{ARM}}\n* [[Republican Party of Armenia]] (HHK)\n* [[Rule of Law (Armenia)|Rule of Law]] (OEK)\n* [[Heritage (Armenia)|Heritage]]\n\n{{BLR}}\n* [[Belarusian Christian Democracy]] (BCD)\n* [[United Civic Party of Belarus]] (AHP)\n* The Movement for Freedom (MFF)<ref>[http://pyx.by/eng/news/5657/ The MFF is admitted to the EPP]. http://pyx.by. Retrieved on 15 January 2019.</ref>\n\n{{BIH}}\n* [[Party of Democratic Action]] (SDA)\n* [[Croatian Democratic Union of Bosnia and Herzegovina]] (HDZBiH)\n* [[Party of Democratic Progress]] (PDP)\n* [[Croatian Democratic Union 1990]] (HDZ 1990)\n\n{{FIN}}\n* [[Christian Democrats (Finland)|Christian Democrats]] (KD)\n\n{{GEO}}\n* [[United National Movement (Georgia)|United National Movement]] (UNM)\n* [[European Georgia]]\n\n{{ITA}}\n* [[South Tyrolean People's Party]] (SVP)\n* [[Trentino Tyrolean Autonomist Party]]\n\n{{flag|Kosovo}}\n*[[Democratic League of Kosovo]] (LDK)\n\n{{MDA}}\n* [[Liberal Democratic Party of Moldova]] (PLDM)\n* [[Dignity and Truth Platform Party]] (PPDA)\n* [[Party of Action and Solidarity]] (PAS)\n\n{{NOR}}\n* [[Christian Democratic Party (Norway)|Christian People's Party]] (KrF)\n\n{{SMR}}\n* [[Sammarinese Christian Democratic Party]] (PDCS)\n\n{{UKR}}\n* [[Democratic Alliance (Ukraine)|Democratic Alliance]]{{citation needed|date=May 2019}}\n* [[European Solidarity]]<ref>{{cite news |title=\u0404\u0432\u0440\u043e\u043f\u0435\u0439\u0441\u044c\u043a\u0430 \u043d\u0430\u0440\u043e\u0434\u043d\u0430 \u043f\u0430\u0440\u0442\u0456\u044f \u043f\u0440\u0438\u0439\u043d\u044f\u043b\u0430 \u043f\u0430\u0440\u0442\u0456\u044e \u041f\u043e\u0440\u043e\u0448\u0435\u043d\u043a\u0430 |url=https://www.eurointegration.com.ua/news/2019/09/10/7100570/ |accessdate=10 September 2019 |work=\u0404\u0432\u0440\u043e\u043f\u0435\u0439\u0441\u044c\u043a\u0430 \u041f\u0440\u0430\u0432\u0434\u0430 |date=10 September 2019 |language=uk}}</ref>\n* [[Batkivshchyna|Fatherland]] (since 2008)\n* [[Self Reliance (political party)|Self Reliance]] (since 2019)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.epp.eu/press-releases/epp-political-assembly-remains-committed-to-spitzenkandidat-process-welcomes-new-ukrainian-parti