ata/ghl002.mbr/lista?liid=43&dfom=20150001|title=\u00c5rslista Singlar \u2013 \u00c5r 2015|publisher=[[Sverigetopplistan]]|accessdate=January 6, 2018}}</ref>\n| 63\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| UK Singles (Official Charts Company)<ref>{{cite web|title=The Official Top 40 Biggest Songs of 2015 revealed|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-songs-of-2015-revealed__13270/|accessdate= January 4, 2016}}</ref>\n| 25\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| US ''Billboard'' Hot 100<ref>{{cite web|title=Hot 100: Year End 2015|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2015/hot-100-songs|website=Billboard|publisher=billboard.com|accessdate=December 9, 2015}}</ref>\n| 10\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2015/hot-r-and-and-b-hip-hop-songs|title=Year-end - US Hot R&B/Hop-hop Songs|work=Billboard|accessdate=December 9, 2015}}</ref>\n| 4\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| US Hot R&B Songs (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2015/hot-r-and-and-b-songs|title=Hot R&B Singles: Year-End|work=Billboard|accessdate=December 11, 2015}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| US Mainstream Top 40 (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|title=Pop Songs Year End 2015|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2015/pop-songs|work=Billboard|accessdate=December 13, 2015}}</ref>\n| 29\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| US Rhythmic (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|title=Rhythmic Songs Year End 2015|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2015/rhythmic-songs|work=Billboard|accessdate=January 6, 2018}}</ref>\n|5\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Chart (2016)\n! Position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia Urban (ARIA)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/annual-charts/2016/urban-singles-chart|title=ARIA Top 50 Urban Singles 2016|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|accessdate=January 6, 2017}}</ref>\n| 19\n|-\n! scope=\"